					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12774784#post-4430504</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12774784/scp-4509#post-4430504</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 24 Nov 2019 09:45:05 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>weedfire24</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4588247</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This. I'm not even sure if it even has potential to be written better since the concept is so undeviating from start to finish. It reads more like a tale than a SCP. Its too barebones for me to really enjoy. The &quot;gnome&quot; is the real anomaly here, yet the Foundation tries to classify the Windigo as 4509?</p> <p>-1 from me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12774784#post-4422376</guid>
