				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-12774784/scp-4509#post-4413220</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 02 Nov 2019 21:16:26 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>writteninwhitespace</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5648639</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Speaking as a non-Native American, after some quick research I was able to discover that in Native American mythology, wendigos do not have antlers. This is a minor part of your article from what I was able to gather, but it felt important to mention. Indigenous Foundation members are very much encouraged to tell me if I am wrong.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
